{"tid":1215664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文：拒絕以修例為前提的個案移交　不作惡法幫兇","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:44:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1233,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"a4174144f9d69619a4a42bcc24a193d1898c7ba8","tid":1215664,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462647_1_L_20190613155232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462647_1_L_20190613155232.jpg&h=26da54d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在台北，蔡英文總統表示，香港修訂《逃犯修例》有侵害人權的疑慮，希望特區政府認真看待抗爭的訴求，與民眾對話及溝通，不應倉促通過相關修訂。她說，台灣不接受香港修例，也拒絕以修例為前提的個案移交，不願成為惡法的幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文在總統府見傳媒時又說，事件讓台灣民眾最深的感受是一國兩制不可信，尤其是對民主化的台灣，一國兩制是不可能被接受。她認為香港的抗爭，令台灣民眾更珍惜現有的民主制度和生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文說，看到香港的警方以催淚氣體及橡膠子彈對待民眾，感到震驚及不忍。她又提到，今日有幾名香港在台灣的學生到總統府就事件陳情，總統府秘書長陳菊已聆聽他們的意見。"},{"pid":"7eed6728f6bc1a4af24b55823a4bbb174f76fed9","tid":1215664,"uid":20816,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2358c9f6f961fe7c8c56e0ec553f530dab0497f","tid":1215664,"uid":61529,"like":545,"dislike":1,"score":544,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"今次助攻晒你啦 台灣人醒返次唔好輸呀"},{"pid":"5f351b005cd2d69256d06d8cdced329c335253b9","tid":1215664,"uid":80455,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57401703516176835ddbf7e455321d6f97b2b54d","tid":1215664,"uid":22131,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"仆街林鄭答喇嘛"},{"pid":"bc9bc6a8f5b9fc6a13c7758b55f2043e0fb78240","tid":1215664,"uid":73381,"like":72,"disli